replies.body:
Friggin ISP's shutting off the internet at the worst possible time....
{{sticker:zombie-brand-facepalm}} 

Those "attempting to reconnect" after your internet service came back might be caused if some of your network settings were reset. Let's make sure to update those [**network settings**](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/articles/201752664-Troubleshooting-Connection-Issues) first, and test those changes in a custom or practice match.
